data.description: Move in condition with Luxury Vinyl Planking & tile through out. Upgraded kitchen with top of line appliances, recessed lighting through out, large pantry. Mud room with built-in organizer. Main level laundry room. Large great room with cathedral ceilings, french  doors leading to rear trex deck.  Formal living room & dining room. Small main level bedroom could be an office if needed. Upper level consists of large primary bedroom with walk in closet. 2 additional sizable bedrooms with closet organizers, and hallway full bath. 2 car garage was converted to additional living space. Garage could be used for storage, motorcycle or maybe small car. Easy commute to AFB and D.C. metro area.
